    "name": "Grand Signature Resort Hoi An by M Village",
    "detail": "We stayed here for 4 nights when we were in Hoi An. We absolutely loved Hoi An Silk Village - it has been the best hotel we have stayed in during our Asia trip so far. The service was over the top - the staff was incredibly friendly and went out of their way to help us out. They knew it was our anniversary and the first day provided a cake and flowers for us in our room. The rooms were new, clean, wonderfully decorated, and the bed and air conditioning were perfect. We also loved the shower. Having free bikes to ride to town and use during the day was great as well. They also have an awesome pool and a free shuttle to the beach and their own private area with chairs and towels for you. Lastly, the breakfast was delicious and offered a wide variety of options. Overall, everything about our stay here was positive - we would highly recommend it to anyone coming to Hoi An. High value for the cost of the hotel. Thank you Hoi An Silk Village for such a positive experience and for your incredible service! You all are doing a wonderful job. ",
